        {
            "title": "意圖向習近平進一步施壓 川普尋求在亞洲簽署關鍵礦產協議",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國高級官員透露，總統唐納德·川普希望在他的亞洲之行中與貿易夥伴簽署經濟和關鍵礦產協議，以在與中國國家主席<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:習近平;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/習近平\">習近平</a>進行舉足輕重的會晤前加大對北京方面的壓力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">總統啟程前美國官員周五向記者吹風，稱川普將尋求有助於釋放該地區資源潛力、可打造更可靠的產業供應鏈的協議，同時也著眼促進全球成長並確保更多投資進入美國。官員們沒有透露總統所尋求協議的具體內容。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普此行將前往馬來西亞出席東協峰會，然後赴日本進行國事訪問和去韓國參加亞太經合組織峰會，最後再與習近平舉行面對面的會晤。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-eceaa358-e3d6-3a15-9370-2485be0d4ffd-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在見面之前，川普也在力爭提升自己的談判地位。美國貿易代表周五早些時候宣布啟動對中國是否遵守了雙方第一階段經貿協定的301條款調查，為進一步對華加徵關稅打開了大門。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">除了稀土之外，川普還想要說服習近平恢復購買美國大豆、打擊芬太尼流通，並就結束烏克蘭戰爭向俄羅斯總統弗拉基米爾·普丁施壓。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">俄烏、稀土、核武樣樣都要聊 川普預計將與習近平談妥「一切」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普還將分別與日本首相高市早苗及韓國總統李在明舉行雙邊會談。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Trump Aims to Sign Mineral Deals in Asia to Raise Pressure on Xi</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%84%8F%E5%9C%96%E5%90%91%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E9%80%B2-%E6%AD%A5%E6%96%BD%E5%A3%93-%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%8B%E6%B1%82%E5%9C%A8%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E7%B0%BD%E7%BD%B2%E9%97%9C%E9%8D%B5%E7%A4%A6%E7%94%A2%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0-222631956.html",
